<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洛夫斯先生小声和格雷夫人说了几句话，然后离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的计划正在完美进行中。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格雷夫人说话的时候，她的鼻子兴奋地扭动了几下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么计划？”拇指姑娘问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“洛夫斯先生同意跟你结婚了。”格雷夫人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘震惊了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我不想和他结婚。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别傻了。”格雷夫人皱了皱眉，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“洛弗斯先生很有钱也很亲切，他想跟你结婚是你的福分。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是格雷夫人……”拇指姑娘刚想开口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“闭嘴！”老鼠尖声说道，“要做的事情太多了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天早上，格雷夫人拿来了装着玉米壳的一个大篮子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“洛夫斯先生想让你织一些垫子。”格雷夫人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他脚上毛很多，但是你没有。他的地板很凉的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘看着自己的光脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把鞋子丢在森林的某个地方了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，格雷夫人带来了一些干草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你得做一些扫帚。”格雷夫人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“洛夫斯先生的家里有很多房间，都需要打扫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不在乎。”拇指姑娘大叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他住在地下，我永远都见不到阳光。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么你需要一些灯光。”格雷夫人无视拇指姑娘说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走向衣柜。“这是一盏灯。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的新家会很黑暗，但是你会习惯的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我为什么不能和你在一起？”拇指姑娘问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格雷夫人严厉地说道：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“计划已经定好了，已经太晚了不能再更改了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是那样我不会开心的。”拇指姑娘悲伤地说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然她听到有人轻轻地敲后门，拇指姑娘把门打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“神奇网编织家为您服务。”三只黑蜘蛛说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都穿着前面印有W字母的灰色衬衣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个W都是不同的颜色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“洛夫斯先生叫我们给您做婚纱。”穿着金色W衬衫的蜘蛛说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“洛夫斯先生还真亲切啊！”格雷夫人拍手说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蜘蛛们一边量一边吐丝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不需要太多蕾丝。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>穿着红色W衬衫的蜘蛛说，“她腰很细。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她有点儿瘦。”穿着绿色W衬衫的蜘蛛说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>婚纱渐渐在拇指姑娘身上成型了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着蜘蛛们，眼泪在眼睛里打转。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要呼吸一些新鲜空气。”她马上说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拇指姑娘！”格雷夫人严肃地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是拇指姑娘已经跑到外面了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面虽然冷，但是很晴朗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经厌烦了每个人告诉我该怎么做。”她对着天空大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想结婚！我不想住在地底下！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是没有人听见拇指姑娘说的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>